  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the mussels and clams under cold water and discard any broken shells.",
    "In a large pot, combine the chicken broth, heavy cream, lemon juice, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Bring the broth mixture to a boil over high heat, then reduce the heat to medium-low and simmer for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the mussels and clams to the pot, cover, and cook for 5 minutes or until the shells open.",
    "Add the shrimp to the pot and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes or until pink and cooked through.",
    "Stir in the sliced scallions and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Serve the seafood and broth in a lacquerware bowl.",
    "Garnish with additional scallions if desired."
  ],
